data.description: Gated & guarded community Southwind. Stunning home with a wall of windows you will love with instant view to the heated gunite pool with fountains & lush landscape. Located near entrance of Southwind. A superb home. Each bedroom has it's own private bath, loft above the garage. Granite kitchen, plenty cabinet space, breakfast bar, large wet bar, bar, refrigerator, ice maker & so much more. Hearth Rm, open living & dining space with soaring ceilings. 3 HVAC units. New leaf guard covers & gutters.
